Краткое описание: Men's Hobes run on the larger side, please view our measurements here to ensure you select the correct size.
Описание: From our original Hobes concept, we've stripped everything back, and built our new men's product from the ground up. The suede is Italian and the shoe is all hand-stitched. The sole, produced from crepe rubber, is incredibly soft to walk on, yet ready for any terrain. Offering lightness, flexibility and versatility, you'll never want to take these guys off.

Краткое описание: Pour conserver la forme d'origine, utilisez des embauchoirs en cèdre ou en bois de hêtre. Cela absorbera l'humidité et atténuera les plis du cuir sur vos souliers.
Описание: La Fango est une desert boots très tendance, le bout de la chaussure arrondi lui donne un look "vintage" tout en nuances. Sa semelle crêpe et sa construction apportent, quant à elles, souplesse et légèreté. Le cuir grenu, renforce le caractère singulier de ces boots.
